      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "CNC (Computer\nNumerical Control)\nElectronics\nRoot question: how do\nCNC (Computer\nNumerical Control)\nelectronics convert a\ntoolpath into safe,\naccurate, diagnosable\nmachine motion?",
