      "text": "Controller Job\nA controller interprets commands, plans\nmotion, schedules outputs, reads inputs, and\nkeeps the machine in a valid operating state.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-f22f5c8d4b05",
      "originalText": "Controller Job\nA controller interprets commands, plans motion, schedules outputs, reads inputs, and keeps the machine in a valid operating state.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "autoResize": true,
      "customData": {
