      "text": "Protection And Faults\nDrives detect overcurrent, voltage\nfaults, overheating, encoder faults,\nstalls, and following error before damage\ngrows.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-2b6e0c39a8f4",
      "originalText": "Protection And Faults\nDrives detect overcurrent, voltage faults, overheating, encoder faults, stalls, and following error before damage grows.",
