      "text": "Resolution Is Not Accuracy\nSteps per unit and encoder counts set command\ngranularity, but they do not prove the tool is\nwhere you think it is.",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 17.5,
      "containerId": "node-58e3a20f52f0",
